<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/semantic-ui/2.5.0/semantic.min.css">
</head>

<body>
    <!-- Navigation (tu peux factoriser plus tard) -->
    <div class="ui inverted menu"
        style="margin: 0; border-radius: 0; background: rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.95); position: fixed; width: 100%; z-index: 1000; backdrop-filter: blur(10px);">
        <div class="ui container">
            <a href="/" class="header item" style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 300;">
                 <%= title.split('-')[0].trim() %>
            </a>
            <a href="/" class="item">Accueil</a>
            <a href="/chambres" class="item">Gérer les chambres</a>
            <a href="/contact" class="item">Contact</a>
            <a href="/clients" class="item">Clients</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div style="padding-top:100px;" class="ui container">
        <div class="ui message">
            <div class="header">
                Modifier la chambre ? <strong>#<%= chambre.numero %></strong> ?
            </div>
            <p>Cette action pourra être modifiée à tout moment. Veuillez insérer le bon numéro de la chambre associée.</p>
        </div>

        <form action="/chambres/update/<%= chambre.id %>" method="POST" style="margin-top: 20px;">
            <button type="submit" class="ui green button">✔︎ Confirmer la modification</button>
            <a href="/chambres" class="ui button">Annuler</a>
        </form>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.0/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/semantic-ui/2.5.0/semantic.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>